             NeoBard Instrument commands


songhelp             -      this help file
farsong              -      special gossip
farsonge             -      special gossip emote
change_instrument    -      change instrument short
crs                  -      create a song in memory
view_song            -      shows stored song
autosong             -      recites stored song
songbreak            -      stops recitation
change_title         -      changes your title
update_instrument    -      updates the instrument
toss_instrument      -      gets rid of this object


Note: to get details on all commands except 
      toss_instrument, songhelp, and songbreak 
      can be found by typing just the command


                               -a Mythos/Saber product